text: Bivalve Oyster Packing Houses and Docks is located in the Bivalve section of Commercial Township, Cumberland County, New Jersey, United States. The Packing Houses and Docks were added to the National Register of Historic Places on February 28, 1996. ==See also== *National Register of Historic Places listings in Cumberland County, New Jersey ==References== Category:Agricultural buildings and structures on the National Register of Historic Places in New Jersey Category:Buildings and structures in Cumberland County, New Jersey Category:Commercial Township, New Jersey Category:National Register of Historic Places in Cumberland County, New Jersey Category:New Jersey Register of Historic Places
